<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Rejoice in Yahweh, you righteous;</para>

<para style="q1">praise is appropriate for the upright.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Give thanks to Yahweh with the harp;</para>

<para style="q1">sing praises to him with the harp of ten strings.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Sing to him a new song;</para>

<para style="q1">play skillfully and sing with joy.</para>
